  "author": "XO_OX Designs",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "description": "Built around the filter's self-oscillation edge — resonance sits at 0.62, just below the feedback threshold, giving the pad a singing quality that borders on instability. At JOURNEY 0.43 this is already vivid and present. The Climax at 0.7 nudges the resonance past the edge: the filter begins to sing on its own, harmonics compound, and the 2-second bloom transforms a controlled sound into pure resonant fever.",
  "tags": ["climax", "demo", "resonant", "filter", "self-oscillation", "journey", "threshold", "prism", "harmonic", "intense"],
  "macroLabels": ["JOURNEY", "BREATHE", "BLOOM", "FRACTURE"],
